dct_title_s: Zee-togten door Thomas Candys na de West Indien : en van daar rondom den gantzen aardkloot gedaan
dct_description_sm: World map, showing the circumnavigation route of Thomas Cavendish; relief shown pictorially. "Met privilegie." In upper right corner: Pag. 1. In lower right corner: Thomas Candisch. From: Naaukeurige versameling der gedenk-waardigste zee en land-reysen na Oost en West-Indiën ... Leyden : Pieter vander Aa, 1707. The collection Naaukeurige versameling ... is divided into 28 "deelen", consisting of 127 parts, each having special t.-p., separate pagination and register. The date of imprint varies: about two-thirds are dated 1706, one-third 1707, five have no date and one is dated 1708. The general title-pages are all dated 1707. cf. Tiele, Nederlandsche bibliographie.
dct_publisher_sm: [Leiden] : Uytgevoord te Leyden door Pieter vander Aa, [1707]
